---
# Project-Specific Memory Settings
# Use per-project to customize memory behavior for specific codebases

# Project Identification
project: my-awesome-project

# Override search mode for this project
defaultSearchMode: both  # Use both semantic and text search

# Project-specific tagging
autoTag:
  enabled: true
  keywords:
    - "frontend"
    - "backend"
    - "api"
    - "database"
  patterns:
    - "bugfix: {component}"
    - "feature:{category}"

# Project-specific retention
retention:
  conversations_days: 180  # Keep for 6 months
  keep_tagged: true
  preserve_critical: true  # Never delete critical conversations

# Project-specific cleanup
cleanup:
  schedule: monthly
  prune_old: true
  keep_project_history: true

# Performance tuning for this project
performance:
  async_operations: true
  max_concurrent_requests: 2
  timeout_seconds: 45

# Search customization
search:
  min_relevance_score: 0.6  # Minimum similarity score
  result_limit: 20  # Max results per search
  include_full_context: false

---

# Project-Specific Configuration

## Usage

Place this file in your project's `.claude/` directory:
```
my-awesome-project/
├── .claude/
│   └── claude-memory-manager.local.md
└── ...
```

## Override Behavior

Project settings override global settings:
- Global settings from `~/.claude/claude-memory-manager.local.md`
- Project settings from `<project>/.claude/claude-memory-manager.local.md`
- Project-specific: `autoTag`, `search`, `retention` sections

## Common Use Cases

### Frontend Projects

```yaml
autoTag:
  enabled: true
  keywords:
    - "react"
    - "component"
    - "ui"
    - "styling"

search:
  include_full_context: true  # UI work needs full context
```

### Backend Projects

```yaml
autoTag:
  enabled: true
  keywords:
    - "api"
    - "database"
    - "migration"
    - "auth"
```

### Research/Exploration

```yaml
retention:
  conversations_days: 730  # Keep for 2 years
  preserve_critical: true
```
